itl.enabler.api.types

Enum UPSDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UPSDataType>
      • itl.enabler.api.types.UPSDataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UPSDataType>

    public enum UPSDataType
extends java.lang.Enum<UPSDataType>
    This is used to indicate the state of an external UPS.

    Not required if the UPS integrates with Windows power management.

    See Also:

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BATTERY_FLAT
